org.semanticweb.owlapi.annotations

Annotation Type OwlapiModule


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
public @interface OwlapiModule
    Annotation for Guice modules providing bindings for the OWLAPI. The bindings can be for any interface. Modules annotated with OwlapiModule can be loaded from the classpath and used to create the main injector. Every module can create its bindings using a different strategy; e.g., hardcoding the contributed mappings or using classpath scanning, ServiceLoader, and similar strategies, to determine the mappings to be used.
    Note: currently, no classpath scan algorithm is used, so modules need to be loaded manually in an injector. Client code can add this functionality if needed.
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    ignazio
